    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video will showcase Staff Management, including:</p><ul><li><p>Creating staff members</p></li><li><p>Editing staff members</p></li><li><p>Terminating staff members</p></li><li><p>Attendance records</p></li><li><p>Staff announcements</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/1_Jo7rGL-gU\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/1_Jo7rGL-gU</a><p> <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-inline\" alt=\"Control - f79824.png\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936785488/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span> </p><h3 id=\"StaffManagementResources(withVideo)-StaffProfileManagement\">Staff Profile Management</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1928921152\" rel=\"nofollow\">Staff Management: Roles and Permissions</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1929379890\" rel=\"nofollow\">Staff Management: Add and Deactivate Staff Profiles</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933836372\" rel=\"nofollow\">Staff Management: Import and Export Staff Profiles</a></p><h3 id=\"StaffManagementResources(withVideo)-LoginandPasswordSettings\">Login and Password Settings</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2024734723\" rel=\"nofollow\">Staff Management Settings</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1928921099\" rel=\"nofollow\">Getting Started: Log In and Password Reset</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1929248790\" rel=\"nofollow\">Staff Management: Update Your Username and Password</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2028634130\" rel=\"nofollow\">Switch Between Staff Profiles Without Logging Out of RepairQ</a></p><h3 id=\"StaffManagementResources(withVideo)-TimecardandAttendance\">Timecard and Attendance</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1928986634\" rel=\"nofollow\">Getting Started: Clock In/Out of RepairQ</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2696282113\" rel=\"nofollow\">Staff Management: View and Adjust Attendance Records</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2933194804\" rel=\"nofollow\">Staff Management: Auto Clock-Out and Overtime Alerts</a></p><h3 id=\"StaffManagementResources(withVideo)-Communication\">Communication</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933803521\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dashboard Announcements</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932525726\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automated Notifications: Inventory Status Changes</a></p><p /><p /><p>START 1.22.X</p>",
